+.TH "COLDFIRE" "1" 
+.SH "NAME" 
+coldfire \(em A Freescale Coldfire 5206 Emulator 
+.SH "SYNOPSIS" 
+.PP 
+\fBcoldfire\fR [\fB\-\-board \fIfilename\fR\fP]  [\fB\-\-timerhack\fP]  
+.SH "DESCRIPTION" 
+.PP 
+\fBcoldfire\fR is a is a Freescale Coldfire 
+5206 Emulator. It currently features all but 5 assembly instructions, 
+a full dBug with extra functionality, both serial ports, the parallel 
+port, interrupts (through telnet sessions), full exception handling, 
+timers and timer interrupts, and full tracing capability. 
+.SH "OPTIONS" 
+.PP 
+These programs follow the usual GNU command line syntax, 
+with long options starting with two dashes (`\-').  A summary of 
+options is included below. 
+.IP "\fB\-\-board\fP \fIfilename\fR         " 10 
+Load board configuration file. 
+.IP "\fB\-\-timerhack\fP         " 10 
+Change the timer so the TRR ticks once per instruction, 
+instead of at an almost correct rate based on cycles 
+executed. 
+.IP "\fB-h\fP, \fB\-\-help\fP         " 10 
+Show summary of options. 
+.IP "\fB-v\fP, \fB\-\-version\fP         " 10 
+Show version of program. 
+.SH "FILES" 
+.PP 
+/usr/share/coldfile/* \- board configuration files 
